      "content": "hey, im so sick of taking warfarin. it feels like i cant even eat a salad without my doctor getting mad about my blood levels lol. is there any way i can just do this naturally? like if i started drinking a bunch of green smoothies with spinach or maybe taking some high dose garlic supplements, would that be enough to keep my blood thin so i dont need the pills anymore?",
